+across `F_SS(1/12)` and `F_SL(1/16)` are:
+`L_tot = 1/4`,
+`L_mirror = 1/12`,
+`L_companion = 1/12`,
+`L_feedback = 1/16`,
+and
+`L_cross = 1/24`.
+
+The inherited Step-4 sheet used
+`Lambda_tot = 3/8`,
+`Lambda_mirror = 1/8`,
+`Lambda_companion = 1/12`,
+`Lambda_feedback = 1/12`,
+and
+`Lambda_cross = 1/12`.
+Only the companion ceiling was already saturated by the recorded friendly
+ledger.
