+The honest Step-5 repair is therefore:
+`Lambda_tot: 3/8 -> 1/4`,
+`Lambda_mirror: 1/8 -> 1/12`,
+`Lambda_companion: 1/12 -> 1/12`,
+`Lambda_feedback: 1/12 -> 1/16`,
+and
